Control Flow

Python Practice 20.2 - At the Boiling Point
temp = int(input())
if temp >= 100:
    print("Boiling")
    
Python Practice 21.2 - Face Control
age = int(input())
if age >= 18:
    print('Allowed')
else:
    print('Sorry')
    
Python Practice 22.2 - Age Groups
age = int(input())
if age <= 11:
    print('Child')
elif age <= 17:
    print('Teen')
else:
    print('Adult')
    
Python Practice 23.2 - Call it Even
x = 0
while x<=10:
  if x%2 == 0:
    print(x)
  x+=1
  
Python Practice 24.2 - Ticket Prices
total = 0
passenger = 0
while passenger < 5:
   age=int(input())
   passenger +=1
   if age <= 3:
      continue 
   elif age>3:
      ticket = 100
      total  += ticket
print(total)

Python Code Project 26 - BMI Calculator
weight = int(input())
height = float(input())
BMI = weight/(height**2)
if (BMI > 0):
    if (BMI < 18.5):
        print('Underweight')
    elif (BMI <25):
        print('Normal')
    elif (BMI <30):
        print('Overweight')
    else:
        print('Obesity')
